      </div>

      <h2 class="content-header">
         When is it?
      </h2>

      <div class="content-box">
         <h3 class="text-center">
            Two days (Saturday and Sunday), 10am-4pm
         </h3>

         <span>
            Interested in helping students learn robotics + computing? <a href="mailto:admin@rowschool.com&subject=Interested in Row School LEGO® Robotics Camp">Contact us</a> today!
